SELECT u.cAddress1, u.cAddress2, u.cAddress3, u.cCity, u.cEmail, u.cFax1, u.cFax2, u.cFirstName, u.cLastName, u.cPhone1, u.cPhone2, u.cPostalCode, u.lCanViewPrices, u.lIsPaper101Grad, u.lTerms, u.dDateLastLogged, u.mMaxOrderAmount, u.mMinOrderAmount, u.cPoList, u.PreferredCatalog, u.OrderConfirmationEmailList, u.UserEmail, u.ReceiveInvoiceEmail, u.InvoiceEmail1, u.InvoiceEmail2, u.lExportToMW, u.PunchoutUser, u.lCanViewPreviewInvoice, u.cNetworkID, u.SC_WebServiceUser, sp.cStateProvince, cn.cCountryName, b.BrandName, c.cBranchCode, cl.cName as cName1, cl.cLocationType, cast(cl.cLocalCustomerNumber as numeric) as cLocalCustomerNumber, cl.cBillToSuffix, cl.cShipToSuffix, ls.cName, cl.cCompanyCode, u.cUserType, --u.EmployeeId, u.nUsers_Id, u.lCanViewReporting, u.lCanOrder, C.cAdditionalEmail FROM xpedx.dbo.Users u (NOLOCK) LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.StateProvinces sp WITH (NOLOCK) ON u.nStateProvinces_id = sp.nStateProvinces_id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.Countries cn WITH (NOLOCK) ON u.nCountries_id = cn.nCountries_id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.CUSTOMERS C WITH (NOLOCK) ON C.nCustomers_id=u.nCustomers_id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.CustomerDivisions CD WITH (NOLOCK) ON C.nCustomers_id=CD.nCustomers_id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.Divisions D WITH (NOLOCK) ON D.nDivisions_id=CD.nDivisions_id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.Brands B WITH (NOLOCK) ON B.Brands_id=D.Brands_id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.UserCustomerLocations UCL WITH (NOLOCK) ON u.nUsers_Id = UCL.nUsers_Id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.CustomerLocations CL WITH (NOLOCK) ON CL.nCustomerLocations_id = UCL.nCustomerLocations_id and CL.nCustomers_id = Cd.nCustomers_id LEFT JOIN xpedx.dbo.LegacySystems LS WITH (NOLOCK) ON LS.nLegacySystems_id = D.nLegacySystems_id
where u.lDeleted = 0 and C.cLocalCustomerNumber not in ('CL','00X8412447','3051284-00') and ( ( u.cNG_datamigration_Flag <> 'M' and u.cUserType in ('BasicUser','CustomerAdmin','MasterAdminUser','MasterBasicUser') and (not cl.cLocalCustomerNumber is null) and ls.cName = 'MAX' and ('#Extract_Type#' = 'F' OR ('#Extract_Type#' = 'C' and C.nCustomers_id in (select nCustomers_id from xpedx.dbo.CustomerXref_NextGen)) ) ) /*OR ( u.cUserType in ('DivAdmin','eCSR','SalesRep','SecurityAdmin','XpedxAdmin','XpedxPub') and (not u.cNetworkID is Null) /*and ((u.dDateLastModified > u.dMigratedTimestamp and u.cNG_datamigration_Flag = 'M') OR (u.cNG_datamigration_Flag <> 'M'))*/ )*/ ) order by u.nUsers_Id, cl.cName, cl.cCompanyCode, cl.cLocalCustomerNumber, cl.cShipToSuffix
